seo: SeaCMS,SQL注入,漏洞检测,安全测试
summary: 检测SeaCMS是否存在SQL延时注入漏洞，黑客可利用该漏洞执行任意SQL语句，如查询数据、下载数据、写入webshell等。
summary_en: Detect whether SeaCMS has SQL delay injection vulnerabilities. Hackers can use this vulnerability to execute arbitrary SQL statements, such as querying data, downloading data, writing webshells, etc.
